---
// Terms of Service page
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Fresh Wax terms of service - rules and guidelines for using our platform.">
  <Header />

  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-container">
      <div class="legal-header">
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: December 2024</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <section>
          <h3>1. About Fresh Wax</h3>
          <p>Fresh Wax is an online music store and community platform specialising in jungle and drum & bass music. We sell digital releases, vinyl records, and branded merchandise. We also provide a platform for DJ mixes and livestreaming.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>2. Account Types</h3>
          <p>When you register for a Fresh Wax account, you automatically receive:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Customer access to purchase releases and merchandise</li>
            <li>Ability to comment on and rate content</li>
            <li>Ability to upload DJ mixes for free listening, download, and community interaction</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Additional roles (Artist/Label, Merch Seller) require admin approval and are subject to additional terms.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>3. DJ Mixes</h3>
          <p>DJ mixes uploaded to Fresh Wax are provided for:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Free listening on the platform</li>
            <li>Free instant download by registered users</li>
            <li>Community engagement through comments and ratings</li>
          </ul>
          <p>DJ mixes are not sold. By uploading a mix, you confirm you have the right to distribute the content and accept responsibility for any copyright issues arising from your upload.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>4. Livestreams</h3>
          <p>Fresh Wax provides livestreaming capabilities for eligible DJs. Regarding livestream content:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>You may record, redistribute, and rebroadcast Fresh Wax livestreams</li>
            <li>This permission is granted provided it does not infringe on copyright laws</li>
            <li>DJs are responsible for ensuring their streamed content complies with copyright regulations</li>
            <li>Fresh Wax is not liable for copyright infringement by DJs or viewers</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>5. Purchases</h3>
          <p>All purchases of digital releases, vinyl, and merchandise are final unless the item is faulty or not as described. Digital downloads are provided immediately upon payment confirmation.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>6. User Conduct</h3>
          <p>You agree to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide accurate information when registering</li>
            <li>Not upload content that infringes copyright or other rights</li>
            <li>Treat other community members with respect</li>
            <li>Not attempt to circumvent platform security or restrictions</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>7. Content Ownership</h3>
          <p>You retain ownership of content you upload (mixes, comments, etc.). By uploading, you grant Fresh Wax a licence to host, display, and distribute your content on the platform.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>8. Termination</h3>
          <p>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms or engage in behaviour harmful to the community.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>9. Changes to Terms</h3>
          <p>We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the platform constitutes acceptance of any changes.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>10. Contact</h3>
          <p>For questions about these terms, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a> through the platform.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-primary, #0a0a0a);
  }

  .legal-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--bg-secondary, #141414);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color, #262626);
  }

  .legal-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color, #262626);
  }

  .legal-header h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary, #fff);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: var(--text-muted, #666);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .legal-content {
    color: var(--text-secondary, #a3a3a3);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-content section {
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .legal-content h3 {
    color: var(--text-primary, #fff);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal-content p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal-content ul {
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .legal-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .legal-content strong {
    color: var(--text-primary, #fff);
  }

  .legal-content a {
    color: #ef4444;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .legal-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
